snippet.title: Might & Magic Duel of Champions PC & iPad Open Beta Launch [UK]
snippet.description:
Might & Magic Duel of Champions is a free-to-play online card game set in the Might & Magic fantasy universe. 

Choose a Hero and build his army with Unit, Spell and Fortune cards to defeat your opponents in epic card battles.
